  lines:
  - text: See? Walked out without a scratch thanks to your <b><sprite=9> HELMETS</b>.
    npcImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8726e1acf043ab7458c657ccfd002abf, type: 3}
    playerImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8726e1acf043ab7458c657ccfd002abf, type: 3}
    buttonText: Helmets?
    highlightID: 0
  - text: You already have 3 <b><sprite=9> HELMETS</b> equipped, shown on your <color=#67f834><b>left</b></color>.
      You can also cycle between them with <b>keys [1] and [2]</b>.
    npcImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a45fb2ba6b66d0248841039a01baca32, type: 3}
    playerImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8726e1acf043ab7458c657ccfd002abf, type: 3}
    buttonText: And those numbers?
    highlightID: 2
  - text: The top number <sprite=18> shows it's <sprite=16> <b>HEALTH</b>. Get hit
      or break a combo and it will decrease. Reach 0 and it will <sprite=22> <b>break</b>
      and be <b><color=red>unusable!</color></b>
    npcImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: aef12474eae64534fbef8c36a460a916, type: 3}
    playerImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a45fb2ba6b66d0248841039a01baca32, type: 3}
    buttonText: And the small one?
    highlightID: 2
  - text: The small number on the right <sprite=19> shows it's <sprite=15> <b>POWER</b>.
      It determines how much <b>damage</b> you make to enemies and how many <b>resources</b>
      you collect from each block you mine.
    npcImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a45fb2ba6b66d0248841039a01baca32, type: 3}
    playerImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8726e1acf043ab7458c657ccfd002abf, type: 3}
    buttonText: Got it!
    highlightID: 2
  - text: There are around <b>20+ <sprite=20> EPIC HELMETS</b> with different abilities,
      health and power combinations to discover and <b><sprite=11> CRAFT!</b>
    npcImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: a45fb2ba6b66d0248841039a01baca32, type: 3}
    playerImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8726e1acf043ab7458c657ccfd002abf, type: 3}
    buttonText: Gotta catch'em all!
    highlightID: 0
